crooks I see. I never did learn how to write it or

24:21.822 --> 24:25.125
read it either. Only thing I can read is Dear 
Friend, Dear Friend, Leave a Friend. That's all I

24:29.229 --> 24:30.370
can read. Well, when you left the mines, did you 
pretty much forget about the mines? Or did you keep

24:35.455 --> 24:36.936
in contact? Yeah, we kind of forgot after a while. 
Well, mostly all the mines closed up then, didn't

24:41.180 --> 24:43.842
they? Yeah.

24:47.056 --> 24:49.720
Yeah, they closed up in the Depression, pretty 
much. They closed up during the 1930s. They got oil

