Well, we couldn't get in that age. We ain't going to 
be much of anything, I presume. Y'all look pretty

28:12.593 --> 28:13.915
spry to me. What happened to your old house there at 
the Vogel Mine? After a while, they tore it down.

28:21.148 --> 28:22.570
When grandmother died, They tore it down and built 
another room onto her house. That's Grandmother

28:27.768 --> 28:29.109
Vogel. Uh-huh. And we moved in there. We lived in 
