31:36.258 --> 31:40.885
two weeks paid that doctor 50 cents. And if 
somebody gets sick and he had to come on out, it

31:41.105 --> 31:45.011
would cost him any more, you know. It wouldn't cost 
him? No, any more, no. Anyway, where's the

31:47.354 --> 31:48.976
medicine? At the drugstore. It was made out there. 
